    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li>This story captures the efforts to E2E test the LAQ360 CSV extract process through the Admin Portal.
	<ul>
		<li>Admin Portal Dependency.</li>
		<li>CSV extract to be clarified.</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>AC:
	<ul>
		<li>Within the Admin Portal, in test and stage, create a project and assign the LAQ360 to self-rater(s), raters, and leaders.</li>
		<li>Successfully generate reports from Envisia and ensure the scoring &amp; reporting is consistent with what the Research Team &amp; Data Team seek</li>
		<li>Document the results and notify the PO.</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

