    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li>This story captures the efforts to define the CSV Report Structure Template for LAQ360.
	<ul>
		<li>Scope of work here would be to conclude on the specific column names and conclude on that data and its format to be inserted</li>
		<li>Envisia provides a feed with everything the Research Team needs. The CSV file provided by Anureka’s Data Team has everything they receive in Snowflake.</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><span class="nobr"><a href="/rest/api/3/attachment/content/600893" title="HSI_AssessmentSummary_Envisia_20260601000507.xlsx attached to AS-8174" data-attachment-type="file" data-attachment-name="HSI_AssessmentSummary_Envisia_20260601000507.xlsx" data-media-services-type="file" data-media-services-id="0cd4c0aa-ab00-4eb3-8ad4-41dd19829123" rel="noreferrer">HSI_AssessmentSummary_Envisia_20260601000507.xlsx<sup><img class="rendericon" src="/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif" height="7" width="7" align="absmiddle" alt="" border="0"/></sup></a></span></li>
	<li>Nadim followed up with Keith to see if he has file for the Research Team to share.</li>
	<li>AC: Ensure the JSON file has everything needed for a CSV extract.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

    <br/>

    <table cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" align="center">
    <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#bbbbbb" width="1%" nowrap align="center">
            &nbsp;<font color="#ffffff"><b>Comments</b></font>&nbsp;
        </td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    </table>

    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" class="grid" style="margin: 0;">
                <tr id="comment-header-1277697"><td bgcolor="#f0f0f0">
            Comment by  
                                                    
                
        
            <a class="user-hover" rel="636bfd21db77c018ecd1c2b1"
                id="word_commented_636bfd21db77c018ecd1c2b1"
                href="https://heidrick.atlassian.net/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?accountId=636bfd21db77c018ecd1c2b1">
                    Bhosale, Sudhir
                </a>

                                        <font size="-2">
            [
                <font color="#336699">11/Jun/26</font>

                            ]
            </font>

        </td></tr>
        <tr id="comment-body-1277697"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p>We are good with the creation and the report structure. The remaining work is to create the aggregation query to fetch the required information from the respective collection or API. For example, we are currently retrieving data from the assessments collection within the score sets.</p>

<p>Once the template is created, we need to verify the CSV attachment flow and confirm that it is working as expected.</p>

<p>Please find the attached snapshot for reference.</p>

<p><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://heidrick.atlassian.net/rest/api/3/attachment/content/599218" alt="image-20260611-110337.png" width="852" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></p>

<p>cc <a href="https://heidrick.atlassian.net/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?accountId=63db0a30bf837c6893d7ef46" class="user-hover" rel="63db0a30bf837c6893d7ef46" data-account-id="63db0a30bf837c6893d7ef46" accountid="63db0a30bf837c6893d7ef46" rel="noreferrer">Jain, Saloni</a> <a href="https://heidrick.atlassian.net/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?accountId=637ef8079960988ef6bdf2f0" class="user-hover" rel="637ef8079960988ef6bdf2f0" data-account-id="637ef8079960988ef6bdf2f0" accountid="637ef8079960988ef6bdf2f0" rel="noreferrer">Vagare, Amol</a> <a href="https://heidrick.atlassian.net/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?accountId=712020%3Afe2f43ac-2d6f-4e36-b148-7e8e65ba67db" class="user-hover" rel="712020:fe2f43ac-2d6f-4e36-b148-7e8e65ba67db" data-account-id="712020:fe2f43ac-2d6f-4e36-b148-7e8e65ba67db" accountid="712020:fe2f43ac-2d6f-4e36-b148-7e8e65ba67db" rel="noreferrer">Jaiswal, Nitesh</a> <a href="https://heidrick.atlassian.net/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?accountId=712020%3Abcb60ba9-1827-4942-ba33-c13752facf17" class="user-hover" rel="712020:bcb60ba9-1827-4942-ba33-c13752facf17" data-account-id="712020:bcb60ba9-1827-4942-ba33-c13752facf17" accountid="712020:bcb60ba9-1827-4942-ba33-c13752facf17" rel="noreferrer">Tidke, Deepali</a> </p>
